{"article_id":"2ev1tLu2Ek6NCWbb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Two Republican senators","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"who this week said","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"they would be hesitant to proceed with a vote on Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"until they had a chance","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"to hear from a woman","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"accusing him of sexual assault","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"are strongly encouraging the accuser to appear at a scheduled hearing next week .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Sens . Bob Corker , R-Tenn. , and Jeff Flake , R-Ariz. , both called for a delay on Kavanaugh 's confirmation vote ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"which had been scheduled for Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"after Palo Alto University professor Christine Blasey Ford came forward publicly as Kavanaugh 's accuser in The Washington Post over the weekend .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Judiciary Committee Chairman Sen. Chuck Grassley , R-Iowa , tried to arrange phone calls with Kavanaugh and Ford","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to discuss the allegation","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and eventually agreed to schedule a public hearing on Monday","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"with both parties","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"invited to testify .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"But Ford 's attorney , Debra Katz , has since said","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that her client wants an FBI investigation into the alleged incident","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"before testifying .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"On Wednesday , Grassley sent a series of tweets","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"in which he said","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"`` Ford should n't be threatened or insulted , ''","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that she `` deserves to be heard ''","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"and that he expects his `` colleagues on both sides of the aisle to be respectful","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"& treat the situation with the sensitivity","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"it deserves . ''","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"But he also dismissed the calls for an FBI investigation .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Grassley said","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"committee investigators are `` following up on the leads from Dr. Ford 's allegations ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and `` no other OUTSIDE investigation is necessary . ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Ford alleges","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Kavanaugh held her down","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"and tried to remove her clothes at a party","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"when they were both in high school .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Kavanaugh has strongly denied the accusation .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Corker said in a tweet early Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"that Grassley `` took immediate action","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to ensure","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"both Dr. Ford and Judge Kavanaugh have the opportunity","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"to be heard , in public or private . ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"`` Republicans extended a hand in good faith , ''","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"`` If we do n't hear from both sides on Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"let 's vote . ''","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake , R-Ariz. ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"who sits on the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"strongly urged Ford to accept the Senate 's invitation","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to speak on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` When Dr. Ford came forward ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"I said","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"that her voice should be heard","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"and asked the Judiciary Committee to delay its vote on Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"It did so , ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Flake said in a tweet Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` I now implore Dr. Ford to accept the invitation for Monday in a public or private setting .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The committee should hear her voice . ''","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"President Donald Trump also indicated","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he hopes","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Ford attends Monday 's scheduled hearing .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"`` I really would want to see what she has to say , ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Democrats are `` hurting somebody ' s life very badly '' with the allegation against Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"'What happens at Georgetown Prep , stays at Georgetown Prep , '","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"Kavanaugh joked in 2015","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"'Uncontrollable male passion ' :","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Writings of Brett Kavanaugh 's classmate under scrutiny","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":137,"left":0,"right":136,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":136,"left":130,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":86,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":78,"right":85,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":75,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":72,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":70,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":76,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":82,"right":84,"relati